<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>Privacy Policy – TheDevStudio</title>
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@400;500;600;700;800&display=swap" rel="stylesheet"/>
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.5.0/css/all.min.css"/>
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/legal.css" />
</head>
<body>
  <%- include('../partials/navbar') %>

  <div class="legal-container">
    <div class="legal-hero">
      <div class="legal-badge">
        <i class="fa-solid fa-shield-halved"></i>
        <span>Last Updated: May 2026</span>
      </div>
      <h1>Privacy Policy</h1>
      <p>Your privacy is our priority. Learn how we collect, use, and protect your data.</p>
      <a href="/auth/signup" class="legal-back"><i class="fa-solid fa-arrow-left"></i> Back to sign up</a>
    </div>

    <div class="legal-content">
      <section class="legal-section">
        <h2>1. Introduction</h2>
        <p>TheDevStudio is committed to protecting your privacy. This Privacy Policy explains how we collect, use, disclose, and safeguard your information when you use our platform.</p>
        <div class="highlight-box">We comply with the General Data Protection Regulation (GDPR) and other applicable data protection laws.</div>
      </section>

      <section class="legal-section">
        <h2>2. Information We Collect</h2>
        <h3>Personal Information</h3>
        <ul>
          <li>Name and contact details (email, phone if provided)</li>
          <li>Account credentials (password stored securely using bcrypt)</li>
          <li>Profile information (picture, bio, optional details)</li>
        </ul>
        <h3>Learning and Activity Data</h3>
        <ul>
          <li>Course enrollments and completion status</li>
          <li>Challenge submissions and quiz results</li>
          <li>Learning progress and engagement metrics</li>
        </ul>
        <h3>Instructor Verification Data</h3>
        <ul>
          <li>Professional details (job title, company, experience)</li>
          <li>Verification documents (resumes, certificates, ID)</li>
          <li>Portfolio links (GitHub, LinkedIn, etc.)</li>
        </ul>
        <h3>Technical Data</h3>
        <ul>
          <li>Device information (browser, OS, device type)</li>
          <li>Session data (IP address, session tokens, usage logs)</li>
          <li>Cookies and analytics data</li>
        </ul>
      </section>

      <section class="legal-section">
        <h2>3. How We Use Information</h2>
        <ul>
          <li>Account management and service delivery</li>
          <li>Progress tracking and learning analytics</li>
          <li>Instructor application review</li>
          <li>Platform improvement and user experience</li>
          <li>Security and fraud prevention</li>
          <li>Legal compliance</li>
        </ul>
      </section>

      <section class="legal-section">
        <h2>4. Sharing of Information</h2>
        <div class="warning-box">We do not sell, rent, or trade your personal information to third parties for marketing purposes.</div>
        <h3>We may share with:</h3>
        <ul>
          <li>Service providers (hosting, payment processors, email services)</li>
          <li>Legal authorities when required by law</li>
          <li>Instructors for courses you are enrolled in</li>
        </ul>
      </section>

      <section class="legal-section">
        <h2>5. Data Retention</h2>
        <ul>
          <li>Account data: 2 years after account closure</li>
          <li>Learning progress: Until you request deletion</li>
          <li>Verification documents: 1 year after application decision</li>
          <li>Session data: 90 days for security and analytics</li>
          <li>Payment records: 7 years for tax compliance</li>
        </ul>
      </section>

      <section class="legal-section">
        <h2>6. Security Measures</h2>
        <ul>
          <li>Password hashing with bcrypt</li>
          <li>HTTPS/TLS encryption for data in transit</li>
          <li>Strict access controls and authentication</li>
          <li>Regular security audits and monitoring</li>
          <li>Secure storage environments</li>
        </ul>
      </section>

      <section class="legal-section">
        <h2>7. Your Rights (GDPR)</h2>
        <ul>
          <li>Right to access your personal data</li>
          <li>Right to rectification of inaccurate data</li>
          <li>Right to erasure ("right to be forgotten")</li>
          <li>Right to restrict processing</li>
          <li>Right to data portability</li>
          <li>Right to object to processing</li>
          <li>Right to withdraw consent</li>
        </ul>
        <p>Contact privacy@thedevstudio.com to exercise these rights. We respond within 30 days.</p>
      </section>

      <section class="legal-section">
        <h2>8. Cookies and Sessions</h2>
        <h3>Types of Cookies:</h3>
        <ul>
          <li>Session cookies for login and platform functionality</li>
          <li>Analytics cookies to understand user interactions</li>
          <li>Preference cookies to remember your settings</li>
        </ul>
      </section>

      <section class="legal-section">
        <h2>9. International Data Transfer</h2>
        <p>Your information may be transferred to countries other than your own. We ensure appropriate safeguards are in place to protect your data in accordance with GDPR requirements.</p>
      </section>

      <section class="legal-section">
        <h2>10. Policy Changes</h2>
        <p>We may update this Privacy Policy. We will notify you of significant changes via email and/or prominent notice on the platform.</p>
      </section>

      <section class="legal-section">
        <h2>11. Contact Us</h2>
        <div class="contact-info">
          <p><strong>Email:</strong> <a href="mailto:privacy@thedevstudio.com">privacy@thedevstudio.com</a></p>
          <p><strong>Support:</strong> <a href="mailto:support@thedevstudio.com">support@thedevstudio.com</a></p>
          <p><strong>Response Time:</strong> Within 30 days</p>
        </div>
      </section>
    </div>
  </div>

 
</body>
</html>